OL,6,FLaura Whitmore says she wants to "set
OL,7,Fthe record straight" by speaking out,
OL,8,Fas ITV News' Ellie Pitt explains
OL,10,FTV presenter Laura Whitmore has
OL,11,Falleged that she was subjected to
OL,12,F'inappropriate behaviour' during her
OL,13,Ftime on Strictly Come Dancing.
OL,15,FThe former Love Island host, 39, was
OL,16,Fpartnered with professional dancer
OL,17,FGiovanni Pernice and was the seventh
OL,18,Fcelebrity eliminated in the 2016
OL,19,Fseries.
