OL,3,CLaura Whitmore alleges 'inappropriate
OL,4,Cbehaviour' during time on Strictly
OL,6,FWhitmore spoke out in a post online on
OL,7,FSaturday July 27, claiming she "raised
OL,8,Fconcerns" at the time.
OL,10,FGiovanni Pernice has strenuously
OL,11,Fdenied any wrongdoing and previously
OL,12,Frejected "threatening or abusive
OL,13,Fbehaviour" allegations made by
OL,14,FSherlock actress Amanda Abbington, who
OL,15,Fwas partnered with him in 2023 before
OL,16,Fhe exited the show.
OL,18,FIn a post online, Laura Whitmore said
OL,19,Fat the time she thought her alleged
OL,20,Fexperience was "specific to me", but
OL,21,Fnow believes that was wrong.
