OL,6,F"I am not looking for anything, just
OL,7,Fan acceptance that what happened to me
OL,8,Fin the rehearsal rooms during my time
OL,9,Fon BBC Strictly was wrong and that it
OL,10,Fwon't happen to anyone else again",
OL,11,Fshe said in the post.
OL,13,FShe added that she is trying to "set
OL,14,Fthe record straight" by speaking out.
OL,16,FVictim blaming must stop or we will
OL,17,Fnever get better," Whitmore also said.
OL,19,F"I've tried to speak up in the correct
OL,20,Fway.
