OL,6,F"We will continue to respect the
OL,7,Fintegrity of the investigation and
OL,8,Fbelieve it is the right forum for all
OL,9,Fthe evidence to be reviewed.
OL,11,F"As part of the evidence-led review,
OL,12,Fthe BBC has shared the allegations
OL,13,Fthey have been able to substantiate
OL,14,Fwith us.
OL,16,F"They do not resemble Amanda's latest
OL,17,Fallegations, given to Channel 4, in
OL,18,Fany shape or form.
